An internal link to [[start]] and one to a [[some/namespace/page|page]] target.

A named internal link to [[start|the start page]] guides the reader.

External links such as [https://example.com Example] and the bare form https://example.org both work, as does an email like [mailto:user@example.com user@example.com].

An interwiki shortcut points at [https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wiki Wiki] for background reading.
